    <section name="Overview">
      <p>
        <strong>Commons</strong> provides a set of libraries, services
        and APIs meant to be the most basic, general-purpose
        horizontal module for all <i>ACM-SL</i> projects.
      </p>
      <subsection name="Status">
        <p>
          <strong>Commons</strong> contains:
          <ul>
            <li><b>regexpplugin</b>: API to request <i>regexp</i>
            services independently of the specific engine used.</li>
            <li><b>patterns</b>: Interfaces and some implementations
            of desing patterns.</li>
            <li><b>versionable</b>: API to export and manage
            per-file <i>CVS</i> information.</li>
            <li><b>utils</b>: General-purpose helper classes.</li>
            <li><b>automata</b>: API to model stateful behaviours.</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </subsection>
    </section>

